text: Aaron James Horvath (born August 19, 1980) is an American animator, television writer, producer, and director. He is best known for co-developing Teen Titans Go! with Michael Jelenic and the creator of The Misfortune of Being Ned for Cartoon Network. == Other websites == * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:American television writers Category:American television producers Category:American television directors Category:American animators Category:People from Orange County, California
